<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.8">
<l>kuṉṟa mēnti kuḷirmaḻai kāttava</l>
<l>ṉaṉṟu ñāla maḷanta pirāṉparaṉ</l>
<l>ceṉṟu cērtiru vēṅkaṭa māmalai</l>
<l>yoṉṟu mētoḻa namviṉai yōyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who protected against the cool rain by holding up the mountain,</l>
<l>the lord who measured the world that day, the Highest one,</l>
<l>when we go, join [and] worship his sacred great Vēṅkaṭam mountain</l>
<l>as the only one our karma will come to an end.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
